<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="count-on-upon">count on / upon</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>依靠；依赖；指望</strong></h4>
<p>to depend on sb or sth, especially in a difficult situation：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>That was the first time Dad had counted on me in a moment of emergency.
这是父亲第一次在危急时刻依赖我。</p><footer>2011 重庆</footer></div></div>